17
00:02:33,120 --> 00:02:34,520
and are eventually harvested.

18
00:02:34,520 --> 00:02:36,050
This is the way of the world.

19
00:02:36,710 --> 00:02:38,120
Just like this sweet potato—

20
00:02:38,120 --> 00:02:39,530
do you feel cruel

21
00:02:39,710 --> 00:02:40,960
