00:15:16,960 --> 00:15:17,910
Go back now.

289
00:15:18,960 --> 00:15:19,750
Yes.

290
00:15:24,480 --> 00:15:25,270
Forget it.

291
00:15:25,270 --> 00:15:26,750
Since it's a gift from him,

292
00:15:26,750 --> 00:15:27,750
take it inside.

293
00:15:51,750 --> 00:15:52,570
Your Highness,

294
00:15:52,570 --> 00:15:53,710
are you alright?

295
00:15:54,750 --> 00:15:56,120
Didn't I tell you to protect Nan Rui?

296
00:15:56,120 --> 00:15:57,310
Why are you here?

297
00:15:58,550 --> 00:15:59,950
It's the Crown Princess.

298
00:16:00,120 --> 00:16:01,600
She went to Lord Qianyu's manor.

299
00:16:01,600 --> 00:16:02,840
I don't know what she said to Lord Qianyu,

300
00:16:02,840 --> 00:16:04,390
and she didn't let the Xuanjia Army
follow her.

301
00:16:04,390 --> 00:16:05,720
After that, she left

302
00:16:05,840 --> 00:16:07,870
the manor alone with Lord Qianyu

303
00:16:08,000 --> 00:16:10,260
and had the Xuanjia Army bring this back.

304
00:16:12,150 --> 00:16:12,720
Nan Heng,

305
00:16:12,880 --> 00:16:14,140
you lied to me again.

306
00:16:14,510 --> 00:16:15,440
In the next life,

307
00:16:15,490 --> 00:16:16,860
I will punish you

308
00:16:16,910 --> 00:16:17,960
to kneel on many,

309
00:16:18,070 --> 00:16:19,880
many, many washboards.

310
00:16:20,600 --> 00:16:22,240
Go and gather 200 Xuanjia Army soldiers

311
00:16:22,240 --> 00:16:23,120
to follow me to the city tower.

312
00:16:23,120 --> 00:16:24,250
Yes, Your Highness.

313
00:16:29,270 --> 00:16:30,000
Well,

314
00:16:30,050 --> 00:16:31,410
don't blame me.

315
00:16:31,550 --> 00:16:33,120
If I weren't in such a hurry to get back,

316
00:16:33,120 --> 00:16:35,180
I wouldn't have treated you this way.

317
00:16:35,630 --> 00:16:37,360
Remember what you promised me.

318
00:16:37,630 --> 00:16:40,320
If Yiting and the Song family are
in the slightest danger,

319
00:16:40,320 --> 00:16:41,960
even if I go back,

320
00:16:42,010 --> 00:16:43,250
I won't let you off.

321
00:16:52,340 --> 00:16:59,000
[A Dream of Qingning,
Episode 37, Scene 19]

322
00:17:00,870 --> 00:17:01,840
Qianyu rebels!

323
00:17:01,860 --> 00:17:03,310
Let go of me!

324
00:17:03,600 --> 00:17:04,400
Yiting!

325
00:17:04,400 --> 00:17:05,109
Yimeng.

326
00:17:05,109 --> 00:17:06,050
Yiting!

327
00:17:06,550 --> 00:17:07,589
Yiting.

328
00:17:07,720 --> 00:17:08,680
Are you alright?

329
00:17:10,030 --> 00:17:11,540
Let her go now!

330
00:17:11,560 --> 00:17:14,270
We can't let her go
until this iconic scene is completed.

331
00:17:14,270 --> 00:17:15,200
Yimeng,

332
00:17:15,349 --> 00:17:17,079
Mother is still in their hands.

333
00:17:19,790 --> 00:17:21,240
This has nothing to do with Madam.

334
00:17:21,240 --> 00:17:23,089
Release her right here and right now,

335
00:17:23,089 --> 00:17:24,089
otherwise

336
00:17:24,589 --> 00:17:26,119
I won't cooperate with you.

337
00:17:26,800 --> 00:17:27,839
Relax.

338
00:17:27,920 --> 00:17:29,590
She's perfectly fine in the carriage.

339
00:17:29,590 --> 00:17:30,680
She's just still unconscious

340
00:17:30,680 --> 00:17:31,880
due to some medicine.

341
00:17:32,470 --> 00:17:34,000
You know exactly what I want.

342
00:17:34,000 --> 00:17:36,400
What's in it for me to kill people
at random?

343
00:17:42,380 --> 00:17:43,780
Please cooperate with me

344
00:17:43,800 --> 00:17:45,600
and play out these messy scenes.

345
00:17:45,620 --> 00:17:46,380
I guarantee

346
00:17:46,410 --> 00:17:49,310
I'll safely send them back
in a grand eight-carrier sedan.

347
00:17:49,310 --> 00:17:50,030
Yimeng,

348
00:17:50,110 --> 00:17:50,790
whatever he promises,

349
00:17:50,790 --> 00:17:52,250
don't believe a word of it.

350
00:17:52,310 --> 00:17:54,480
Rather than be held hostage
by someone else,

351
00:17:54,480 --> 00:17:56,270
I'd rather take control of my own fate

352
00:17:56,270 --> 00:17:58,050
and fight him to the bitter end!

353
00:18:03,510 --> 00:18:04,310
Yiting.

354
00:18:05,270 --> 00:18:06,070
I'm sorry.

355
00:18:06,870 --> 00:18:08,200
I dragged you into this.

356
00:18:09,880 --> 00:18:10,750
Don't worry.

357
00:18:11,620 --> 00:18:13,190
I will save you.

358
00:18:13,610 --> 00:18:15,060
After a few hours,

359
00:18:15,880 --> 00:18:16,880
everything

360
00:18:17,110 --> 00:18:18,160
will be over.

361
00:18:18,550 --> 00:18:19,560
Song Yimeng,

362
00:18:19,720 --> 00:18:20,640
what are you going to do?

363
00:18:20,640 --> 00:18:21,810
Tell me.

364
00:18:22,830 --> 00:18:23,640
Song Yimeng!

365
00:18:23,640 --> 00:18:24,200
Song Yimeng!

366
00:18:24,200 --> 00:18:25,450
Don't worry, Yiting!

367
00:18:25,640 --> 00:18:27,600
I won't let anything happen to you!

368
00:18:34,240 --> 00:18:35,600
After the arrows are shot,

369
00:18:35,600 --> 00:18:38,460
I promise I'll push forward the plot
of human swine.

370
00:18:39,550 --> 00:18:40,350
Here.

371
00:18:40,770 --> 00:18:42,080
Tie yourself up.

372
00:18:58,880 --> 00:18:59,740
Your Highness,

373
00:18:59,750 --> 00:19:00,680
the troops are ready.

374
00:19:00,680 --> 00:19:02,480
Why isn't Shangguan He here yet?

375
00:19:03,240 --> 00:19:05,830
This matter concerns the safety
of Song Yiting and Song Yimeng.

376
00:19:05,830 --> 00:19:07,200
Shangguan He will come.

377
00:19:07,640 --> 00:19:08,440
But...

378
00:19:08,590 --> 00:19:09,510
does it have to be him?

379
00:19:09,510 --> 00:19:10,400
Can't I do it?

380
00:19:11,000 --> 00:19:12,200
You have another job.

381
00:19:13,270 --> 00:19:14,070
Chief!

382
00:19:16,890 --> 00:19:17,970
What's wrong?

383
00:19:19,030 --> 00:19:20,110
By the time I arrived,

384
00:19:20,110 --> 00:19:21,790
Song Yiting had already been taken
by the Qianyu Army.

385
00:19:21,790 --> 00:19:23,750
We were even ambushed along the way.

386
00:19:23,750 --> 00:19:25,240
Yunlong and Shanhu stayed behind
to cover my retreat

387
00:19:25,240 --> 00:19:26,770
so that I could make it back.

388
00:19:27,000 --> 00:19:27,750
Chief,

389
00:19:28,270 --> 00:19:30,830
they've mobilized a large number
of the Qianyu Army.

390
00:19:30,830 --> 00:19:31,690
Your Highness,

391
00:19:31,840 --> 00:19:34,000
there are only 300 Xuanjia Army soldiers
in the capital in total,

392
00:19:34,000 --> 00:19:35,530
and some were sent to the palace.

393
00:19:35,530 --> 00:19:36,930
We may not stand a chance.

394
00:19:37,830 --> 00:19:39,350
The border troops are on their way back,

395
00:19:39,350 --> 00:19:40,720
but they'll need at least three days.

396
00:19:40,720 --> 00:19:41,350
Until then,

397
00:19:41,350 --> 00:19:42,280
we must hold out.

398
00:19:43,000 --> 00:19:43,800
Let's do this.

399
00:19:44,310 --> 00:19:45,310
Send someone to Waning River Crescent

400
00:19:45,310 --> 00:19:46,750
to ask the Nightwalker to help
Yunlong and Shanhu.

401
00:19:46,750 --> 00:19:48,590
Tell them to make sure they stall
the Qianyu Army

402
00:19:48,590 --> 00:19:49,940
for at least one hour.

403
00:19:49,970 --> 00:19:51,100
Yes, Your Highness.

404
00:19:57,200 --> 00:19:58,510
You are already like this.

405
00:19:58,510 --> 00:19:59,720
Why don't you go back first?

406
00:19:59,720 --> 00:20:01,640
Leave the "Choice Between Two" to me.

407
00:20:01,640 --> 00:20:02,480
Choose? Like hell.

408
00:20:02,480 --> 00:20:03,030
You save your woman,

409
00:20:03,030 --> 00:20:04,090
and I'll save mine.

410
00:20:04,480 --> 00:20:05,270
Besides,

411
00:20:05,270 --> 00:20:06,820
Chu Li's real target is me.

412
00:20:07,110 --> 00:20:08,070
I have to go.

413
00:20:11,640 --> 00:20:12,440
Fine.

414
00:20:12,920 --> 00:20:13,880
Then tell me

415
00:20:13,880 --> 00:20:14,920
how I can help.

416
00:20:18,770 --> 00:20:28,070
[Yanxing Gate]

417
00:20:39,510 --> 00:20:40,710
It's really snowing.

418
00:20:44,550 --> 00:20:46,070
I told you.

419
00:20:47,590 --> 00:20:49,440
Fate can't be changed.

420
00:20:50,310 --> 00:20:51,550
Any resistance

421
00:20:51,550 --> 00:20:53,080
is just asking for trouble.

422
00:20:53,790 --> 00:20:54,840
In the end,

423
00:20:55,480 --> 00:20:57,030
you'll all come back here

424
00:20:57,350 --> 00:20:58,830
and meet the same fate.

425
00:21:00,200 --> 00:21:02,800
Even if it's the same city tower
and heavy snow,

426
00:21:03,160 --> 00:21:04,560
and even if I'll

427
00:21:05,410 --> 00:21:07,470
go along with the storyline with you,

428
00:21:08,350 --> 00:21:10,280
it doesn't mean that everyone else

429
00:21:10,310 --> 00:21:12,240
will live the way you want them to.

430
00:21:14,240 --> 00:21:15,500
Because everyone here

431
00:21:16,000 --> 00:21:17,600
is no longer that group of...

432
00:21:19,510 --> 00:21:22,240
fictional characters to be manipulated
at will.

433
00:21:31,830 --> 00:21:32,640
General,

434
00:21:33,160 --> 00:21:33,960
they're here.

435
00:21:35,160 --> 00:21:36,680
Bring Song Yiting here.

436
00:21:36,680 --> 00:21:37,350
Yes.

437
00:21:38,550 --> 00:21:39,640
Bring her here!

438
00:21:45,330 --> 00:21:48,250
[Suzhang Gate]

439
00:21:48,350 --> 00:21:50,500
[Yanxing Gate]

440
00:21:51,310 --> 00:21:52,110
Chu Li!

441
00:21:53,640 --> 00:21:54,440
I'm here.

442
00:21:54,770 --> 00:21:55,570
Release her!

443
00:22:03,310 --> 00:22:04,110
Chu Li!

444
00:22:05,200 --> 00:22:06,000
Nan Heng,

445
00:22:06,590 --> 00:22:07,480
listen up.

446
00:22:08,070 --> 00:22:10,440
The antidote for the Emperor
is in my hands.

447
00:22:10,440 --> 00:22:13,750
The evidence proving that Nan Rui
poisoned him is also with me!

448
00:22:13,750 --> 00:22:14,830
If you don't want to become
an eternal sinner

449
00:22:14,830 --> 00:22:17,220
who has killed your father and brother,

450
00:22:17,350 --> 00:22:19,080
shoot the arrows immediately!

451
00:22:19,200 --> 00:22:20,920
You know the ending I want.

452
00:22:22,070 --> 00:22:23,470
Today, at the city tower,

453
00:22:24,000 --> 00:22:26,000
until this "Choice Between Two" scene
is complete,

454
00:22:26,000 --> 00:22:27,040
everything

455
00:22:27,400 --> 00:22:28,880
will never end.

456
00:22:30,830 --> 00:22:31,640
Nan Heng!

457
00:22:34,280 --> 00:22:35,490
In this world,

458
00:22:36,830 --> 00:22:37,640
I've never done anything

459
00:22:37,640 --> 00:22:38,960
to benefit everyone.

460
00:22:40,310 --> 00:22:41,270
But today...

461
00:22:42,850 --> 00:22:44,170
if I can die

462
00:22:45,030 --> 00:22:47,430
for the safety of you
and the Song family...

463
00:22:48,920 --> 00:22:49,720
I'll do it!

464
00:22:51,160 --> 00:22:51,960
Song Yimeng!

465
00:22:53,160 --> 00:22:54,760
You said fate can be changed!

466
00:22:55,720 --> 00:22:57,050
I don't believe in fate,

467
00:22:57,240 --> 00:22:58,220
and neither do you!

468
00:22:58,220 --> 00:22:59,240
Do you hear me?

469
00:23:02,920 --> 00:23:04,310
Saying cheesy lines

470
00:23:04,310 --> 00:23:06,070
at a time like this?

471
00:23:19,160 --> 00:23:20,050
[Yanxing Gate]

472
00:23:27,480 --> 00:23:28,270
Song Yimeng!

473
00:23:28,270 --> 00:23:29,070
Come down!

474
00:23:29,750 --> 00:23:30,510
Hurry!

475
00:23:30,510 --> 00:23:31,240
Go!

476
00:23:31,960 --> 00:23:32,850
Yiting!

477
00:23:46,920 --> 00:23:47,590
Nan Heng.

478
00:24:23,960 --> 00:24:24,960
What do you think?

479
00:24:25,310 --> 00:24:26,440
Other girls have,

480
00:24:26,510 --> 00:24:28,370
and our Yiting deserves the same.

481
00:24:30,030 --> 00:24:30,680
Stay back!

482
00:24:32,600 --> 00:24:33,730
I'll count to three.

483
00:24:34,240 --> 00:24:35,440
Your master's life

484
00:24:35,830 --> 00:24:37,960
in exchange for letting our Yiting go.

485
00:24:38,000 --> 00:24:39,440
If you don't want to,

486
00:24:40,160 --> 00:24:42,480
then let's see whose sword strikes first.

487
00:24:42,480 --> 00:24:43,240
Rong Hua,

488
00:24:43,240 --> 00:24:44,230
save me!

489
00:24:54,790 --> 00:24:56,140
No need to count.

490
00:24:56,720 --> 00:24:57,780
What have you done?

491
00:24:58,270 --> 00:24:59,830
He was Lord Qianyu.

492
00:25:00,030 --> 00:25:01,070
You actually killed him?

493
00:25:01,070 --> 00:25:03,070
My loyalty lies not with Lord Qianyu

494
00:25:03,310 --> 00:25:05,310
but solely with the Junior General.

495
00:25:05,920 --> 00:25:08,440
Soldiers of the Qianyu Army,
heed my command!

496
00:25:08,440 --> 00:25:09,920
Shangguan He, the subordinate
of Nan Heng...

497
00:25:09,920 --> 00:25:10,720
Oh no.

498
00:25:10,720 --> 00:25:11,640
Brutally murdered the general!

499
00:25:11,640 --> 00:25:12,510
Their target is you.

500
00:25:12,510 --> 00:25:13,200
Qianyu Army,

501
00:25:13,200 --> 00:25:14,680
by the order of the Junior General,

502
00:25:14,680 --> 00:25:16,640
eliminate Nan Heng and his followers!

503
00:25:16,640 --> 00:25:18,300
Xuanjia Army, heed my orders!

504
00:25:18,450 --> 00:25:19,690
Today, follow me

505
00:25:20,230 --> 00:25:21,720
and break through at all costs!

506
00:25:21,720 --> 00:25:22,920
-Yes, sir!
-Yes, sir!

507
00:25:24,820 --> 00:25:26,480
[Imperial Study]

508
00:25:31,270 --> 00:25:32,110
General Chu,

509
00:25:32,240 --> 00:25:35,170
how dare you break into
His Majesty's bedchamber...

510
00:25:38,440 --> 00:25:39,450
Chu Guihong,

511
00:25:39,480 --> 00:25:40,760
what do you want?

512
00:25:44,970 --> 00:25:47,200
Of course, I'm here to help His Majesty
defend the throne.

513
00:25:47,200 --> 00:25:49,090
The Crown Prince colluded with Liu Mingxi

514
00:25:49,090 --> 00:25:51,290
and killed the Emperor and his brother.

515
00:25:51,320 --> 00:25:53,170
I had no choice but to kill him

516
00:25:53,270 --> 00:25:54,870
under these circumstances.

517
00:25:55,070 --> 00:25:57,200
Murdered the Emperor and his brother?

518
00:25:57,310 --> 00:25:58,840
What are you talking about?

519
00:26:00,940 --> 00:26:02,160
Before I came,

520
00:26:02,590 --> 00:26:03,880
I had someone finish

521
00:26:03,880 --> 00:26:05,270
today's Emperor's Daily Diary.

522
00:26:05,270 --> 00:26:06,660
"His Majesty, aged and weary,

523
00:26:06,660 --> 00:26:08,720
reminiscing about the late Empress,

524
00:26:09,030 --> 00:26:10,440
chose to appoint a new heir

525
00:26:10,440 --> 00:26:12,880
and passed the throne to
the Eighteenth Prince, Nan Rui.

526
00:26:12,880 --> 00:26:15,310
But the Crown Prince, Nan Heng,
grew resentful

527
00:26:15,310 --> 00:26:16,770
and poisoned His Majesty,

528
00:26:17,240 --> 00:26:19,040
framing Nan Rui as the culprit."

529
00:26:21,880 --> 00:26:23,410
Your Ladyship, do you think

530
00:26:23,720 --> 00:26:24,960
this will make for

531
00:26:25,030 --> 00:26:27,110
a fine chapter

532
00:26:27,400 --> 00:26:28,800
in future history books?

533
00:26:29,310 --> 00:26:30,640
You want to rebel.

534
00:26:31,240 --> 00:26:33,570
Heng will never let you get away
with this!

535
00:26:34,220 --> 00:26:35,830
The Xuanjia Army is still at the border,

536
00:26:35,830 --> 00:26:38,430
while the capital is guarded
by my Qianyu Army.

537
00:26:40,770 --> 00:26:42,010
Your beloved son

538
00:26:42,440 --> 00:26:44,240
is about to die on the city tower.

539
00:26:44,310 --> 00:26:45,750
How will he stop me?

540
00:26:46,390 --> 00:26:48,350
300 Xuanjia Army soldiers in the capital

541
00:26:48,350 --> 00:26:50,520
against 5,000 Qianyu Army soldiers.

542
00:26:50,640 --> 00:26:52,990
Even if Nan Heng had nine lives,

543
00:26:53,830 --> 00:26:55,640
he wouldn't survive this.

544
00:27:01,640 --> 00:27:02,400
Xuanjia Army!

545
00:27:02,400 --> 00:27:03,240
Go up and save them!

546
00:27:03,240 --> 00:27:04,110
-Yes, sir!
-Yes, sir!

547
00:27:04,110 --> 00:27:04,880
-Let's go!
-Let's go!

548
00:27:04,880 --> 00:27:05,590
Fugui!

549
00:27:05,680 --> 00:27:06,810
Take her away first!

550
00:27:08,070 --> 00:27:08,720
No!

551
00:27:08,720 --> 00:27:09,640
Listen to me!

552
00:27:12,310 --> 00:27:13,270
Fugui, hurry!

553
00:27:13,290 --> 00:27:14,360
I can't leave.

554
00:27:14,480 --> 00:27:15,510
If we live, we live together.

555
00:27:15,510 --> 00:27:16,970
If we die, we die together!

556
00:27:20,750 --> 00:27:21,480
Protect her.

557
00:27:21,480 --> 00:27:21,960
Yes.

558
00:27:21,960 --> 00:27:22,590
Nan Heng.

559
00:27:51,090 --> 00:27:52,350
Stop the Xuanjia Army climbing up.

560
00:27:52,350 --> 00:27:54,010
Don't let them rescue anyone!

561
00:28:11,950 --> 00:28:13,310
Shangguan He!

562
00:28:17,200 --> 00:28:18,000
Shangguan He.

563
00:28:18,220 --> 00:28:19,020
Shangguan He.

564
00:28:22,130 --> 00:28:23,000
Shangguan He,

565
00:28:23,000 --> 00:28:24,130
how are you?

566
00:28:28,750 --> 00:28:30,810
I wanted to be the hero and save you...

567
00:28:31,810 --> 00:28:33,160
but I didn't expect to let you

568
00:28:33,160 --> 00:28:34,620
see me at my most pathetic.

569
00:28:36,880 --> 00:28:38,020
I made a mistake.

570
00:28:38,160 --> 00:28:39,070
At a time like this,

571
00:28:39,070 --> 00:28:40,780
